| Orchestration    | Kubernetes              | Same              |
| Data Versioning  | ❌                       | DVC               |
| Model Tracking   | ❌                       | MLflow            |
| Feature Store    | ❌                       | Feast             |
| ML Pipeline      | ❌                       | Kubeflow, Airflow |
| Model Monitoring | Limited                 | Evidently AI      |

